# NixOS

To install GRUB on NixOS, copy the `hardware-configuration.nix` file to the `host` directory and run the command below during the first installation:
```bash
sudo nixos-rebuild switch --flake {path-flake}#{hostname} --install-bootloader
```

## Hyprpanel

Import the Hyprpanel backup file to apply the configurations.

## Update
```
nix flake update
sudo nixos-rebuild switch --flake .#hostname
```

### pc
```
nix flake update
sudo nixos-rebuild switch --flake .#pc
```

### laptop
```
nix flake update
sudo nixos-rebuild switch --flake .#laptop
```
